title: Project S The Series: SPIKE
overview: Last season under the guidance of coach Win, Theppanya's College Volleyball team made it to the finals in which they lost as underdog against St. Sebastian. To make matters worse, Singh, which used to be the ace of their team, decided to leave their team for St. Sebastian. Puen, the new Captain, is very angry about it and makes a promise with their team to return and win the next championship. Coach Win finds a replacement for Singh, however this new guy has troubles of his own.
